    "type": "message",
    "text": "Cool. A not-so-technical friend from a previous job recently asked me for tech support with a curl command. I suggested she use Postman. She said “I had some problems with that” and didn’t elaborate. Eventually we got the curl command working.\n\nThere’s probably some deeper lesson about abstractions here, hehe.",
